#. <section class="sutta" id="sn54.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Ekadhammavagga"
msgstr "1. One Thing"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn54.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Bojjhaṅgasutta"
msgstr "2. Awakening Factors"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.313"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.2:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ānāpānassati, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated it’s "
"very fruitful and beneficial."

msgctxt "sn54.2:1.2"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati kathaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā?"
msgstr ""
"And how is mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated to be very "
"fruitful and beneficial?"

msgctxt "sn54.2:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ānāpānassatisahagataṃ satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ, "
"ānāpānassatisahagataṃ dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … pe … "
"ānāpānassatisahagataṃ upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ "
"virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops mindfulness of breathing together with the "
"awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity, which rely on seclusion, "
"fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go."

msgctxt "sn54.2:1.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati evaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Mindfulness of breathing, when developed and cultivated in this way, is very "
"fruitful and beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.2:1.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
